    <hr style="width: 60%">
    <h3>Pitch your business idea to win funding from Brookwood Capital</h3>
    <h5><strong>When:</strong> 7 July, 2017 at 6:30 PM</h5>
    <h5><strong>Location:</strong> Workshop 17, V&amp;A Waterfront, iX Student Lounge </h5>
    <h5><strong>Deadline to apply:</strong> 12 July, 2017</h5>
