      <h2>Who are we?</h2>
        <h4>We are a young and dynamic team that is quite aggressive in our investment approach. We are not afraid to take a well-researched risk. We focus on finding the “diamonds in the rough,” finding investment opportunities that align with our personal interests. We focus on high potential, purpose driven companies in early stages of development - not just tech start ups. </h4>
